# StorageFlow Consumer Rules

Read `docs/storageflow/STORAGEFLOW.md` before generating StorageFlow code.
Supporting examples and fixes are in `docs/storageflow/examples.md` and
`docs/storageflow/troubleshooting.md`.

Use `IStorageService`, typed policies, official `SFProvider` tokens, streaming
I/O, and `StorageResult`. Never bypass the framework with provider SDKs, expose
provider selection as a raw client string, commit credentials, or invent APIs
outside the documented v1 scope.
